      "    🔍 raw[Note 2/w1]: {   \"visit_date\": {\"value\":\"2024-11-15\",\"unit\":null,\"reference_range\":null,\"exact_quote\":\"Note Date: 2024-11-15\",\"confidence\":\"high\"},   \"age\": {\"value\":\"55\",\"unit\":null,\"reference_range\":null,\"exact_quote\":\"55-year-old female\",\"confidence\":\"high\"},   \"gender\": {\"value\":\"female\",\"unit\":null,\"referen\n",
      "    📋 best-source map: age←w1, albumin←w4, alp←w4, alt←w4, ast←w4, bilirubin_total←w4, creatinine←w4, diagnosis←w1, fib4_reported←w1, fibrosis_stage←w1, gender←w1, glucose←w4, hba1c←w5, inr←w4, medications←w1, nas_score←w5, platelets←w4, visit_date←w1\n",
