    "# ── Cell 6b — Per-Patient Split ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "# Groups EDITED_ROWS by _dob. Each unique DOB gets its own CSV + JSON.\n",
    "# Run after Cell 6 (relies on EDITED_ROWS, LIVER_FIELDS, stem, out_dir).\n",
